          "_name": "menu2",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"menu horizontal-menu\" group=\"Menu\" plugins=\"DropDown, amp-main,amp-sidebar\" global=\"\" once=\"menu\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Logo\" name=\"showLogo\" checked=\"\">\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Logo Height\" inline=\"\" name=\"logoHeight\" min=\"35\" max=\"120\" value=\"45\" step=\"1\" condition=\"showLogo\">\n        <input type=\"range\" title=\"Logo Width\" inline=\"\" name=\"logoWidth\" min=\"35\" max=\"120\" value=\"45\" step=\"1\" condition=\"showLogo\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Brand Name\" name=\"showBrand\" checked=\"\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Menu Items\" name=\"showItems\" checked=\"\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Button(s)\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Sticky\" name=\"sticky\" checked=\"\">\n        <select title=\"Sidebar Side\" name=\"sidebarSide\">\n            <option value=\"left\">Left</option>\n            <option value=\"right\" selected=\"\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Hamburger Color\" name=\"hamburgerColor\" value=\"#0dcd7b\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"menuBgColor\" value=\"#232323\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    \n\n    <nav class=\"navbar navbar-dropdown navbar-expand-lg\" mbr-class=\"{'navbar-fixed-top':sticky}\">\n      <div class=\"brand\" mbr-if=\"showLogo || showBrand\">\n          <span mbr-if=\"showLogo\" class=\"brand-logo\">\n              <amp-img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1-90x60.jpg\" layout=\"responsive\" width=\"45\" height=\"30\" alt=\"Mobirise\" class=\"mobirise-loader\">\n                  <div placeholder=\"\" class=\"placeholder\"></div>\n                  <a href=\"index.html\"><img class=\"mbr-temp\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1-90x60.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title=\"\"></a>\n              </amp-img>\n          </span>\n          <p mbr-text=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showBrand\" class=\"brand-name mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold\" data-app-selector=\".brand-name\">Digipen Music Club</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"navbarSupportedContent\">\n            <button class=\"navbar-toggler mb-2\" type=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#navbarSupportedContent\" aria-controls=\"navbarNavAltMarkup\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\" mbr-if=\"showItems||showButtons\">\n                <div class=\"hamburger\">\n                    <span></span>\n                    <span></span>\n                    <span></span>\n                    <span></span>\n                </div>\n            </button>\n            <ul mbr-menu=\"\" class=\"navbar-nav nav-dropdown\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showItems\" mbr-class=\"{'nav-right': !showButtons,'navbar-nav-top-padding': isPublish &amp;&amp; !showBrand &amp;&amp; !showLogo}\"><li class=\"nav-item dropdown\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link link text-primary dropdown-toggle\" href=\"https://skgtechnology.com/\" data-app-selector=\".nav-link,.dropdown-item\" data-toggle=\"dropdown-submenu\" aria-expanded=\"true\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                        Resources</a>\n                    <div class=\"dropdown-menu\">\n                        <a class=\"text-primary dropdown-item\" href=\"page2.html\" data-app-selector=\".nav-link,.dropdown-item\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Masters</a>\n                        <a class=\"text-primary dropdown-item\" href=\"page1.html\" data-app-selector=\".nav-link,.dropdown-item\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Newcomers</a>\n                    </div>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link link text-primary\" href=\"https://skgtechnology.com/\" data-app-selector=\".nav-link,.dropdown-item\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                        Content</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link link text-primary\" href=\"https://skgtechnology.com/\" data-app-selector=\".nav-link,.dropdown-item\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Schedules</a>\n                </li></ul>\n            \n            <div mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"navbar-buttons mbr-section-btn\"><a class=\"btn btn-sm btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.co\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                  Contact Us\n                </a></div>\n      </div>\n      <button class=\"navbar-toggler hide\" type=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#navbarSupportedContent\" aria-controls=\"navbarNavAltMarkup\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\" mbr-if=\"showItems||showButtons\">\n          <div class=\"hamburger\">\n              <span></span>\n              <span></span>\n              <span></span>\n              <span></span>\n          </div>\n      </button>\n      <button on=\"tap:sidebar.toggle\" class=\"ampstart-btn hamburger\" mbr-class=\"{'sticky-but':sticky}\" mbr-if=\"showItems||showButtons\">\n        <span></span>\n        <span></span>\n        <span></span>\n        <span></span>\n    </button>\n    </nav>\n\n  <!-- AMP plug -->\n    <amp-sidebar id=\"sidebar\" layout=\"nodisplay\" side=\"{{sidebarSide}}\">\n        <div class=\"builder-sidebar\" id=\"builder-sidebar\">\n            <button on=\"tap:sidebar.close\" class=\"close-sidebar\">\n                <span></span>\n                <span></span>\n            </button>\n        </div>\n    </amp-sidebar>\n\n</section>",
          "_cid": "rHflunjDo0",
          "_anchor": "menu2-g",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": true,
          "_once": "menu",
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".ampTabContainer": {
              "display": "flex",
              "-webkit-flex-wrap": "wrap",
              "flex-wrap": "wrap"
            },
            ".tab-button[selected]": {
              "outline": "none",
              "background": "@activeColor"
            },
            ".tab-button": {
              "list-style": "none",
              "-webkit-flex-grow": "1",
              "flex-grow": "1",
              "text-align": "center",
              "cursor": "pointer"
            },
            ".tab-content": {
              "display": "none",
              "width": "100%",
              "order": "1",
              "border": "1px solid @activeColor",
              "padding": "2rem 3rem 3rem",
              "background": "@activeColor",
              "p": {
                "margin": "0",
                "& when (@showTitle)": {
                  "padding": "2rem 0 0"
                },
                "& when not (@showTitle)": {
                  "padding": "0"
                }
              }
            },
            ".tab-button[selected] + .tab-content": {
              "display": "block"
            },
            ".tab-head": {
              "margin": "1rem"
            }
          },
          "_name": "tab1",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section tab1\" group=\"Toggles & Tabs\" plugins=\"amp-main, amp-selector\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        \n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" name=\"activeColor\" value=\"#0dd1ff\">\n        <select name=\"tabsAmount\" title=\"Tabs Amount\">\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"5\">5</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">6</option>\n        </select>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\">\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1920x1175.jpg\" selected>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n        </fieldset>\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <amp-selector role=\"tablist\" layout=\"container\" class=\"ampTabContainer\">\n            <div role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-button\" selected option=\"a\">\n                <h3 class=\"tab-head mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">File Browser</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-content\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">https://soundbridge.io/soundbridge-widgets-file-browser/</h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"></p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-button\" option=\"b\">\n                <h3 class=\"tab-head mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">Filters 1</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-content\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                    https://soundbridge.io/soundbridge-widgets-built-in-effects-1/\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"></p>         \n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-button\" option=\"c\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 2\">\n                <h3 class=\"tab-head mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">Filters 2<br></h3>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-content\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 2\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">https://soundbridge.io/soundbridge-widgets-built-in-effects-2/</h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"></p>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-button\" option=\"d\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 3\">\n                <h3 class=\"tab-head mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">Performance</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-content\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 3\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                    EFFECTIVE ENGAGEMENT\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Dignissimos, pariatur omnis odit, molestias inventore beatae adipisci fugiat fugit itaque minus explicabo iure deserunt corporis minima vitae dicta et libero sit.</span><span>Nihil cumque aspernatur nam fugiat iusto error, distinctio, dolorum explicabo nobis. Voluptatem dolores, laudantium qui aspernatur recusandae velit, molestiae facilis harum itaque quisquam! Porro dolorem, pariatur rerum ullam dolores non?</span></p>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-button\" option=\"e\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 4\">\n                <h3 class=\"tab-head mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">Engagements</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-content\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 4\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                    EFFECTIVE ENGAGEMENT\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Dignissimos, pariatur omnis odit, molestias inventore beatae adipisci fugiat fugit itaque minus explicabo iure deserunt corporis minima vitae dicta et libero sit.</span><span>Nihil cumque aspernatur nam fugiat iusto error, distinctio, dolorum explicabo nobis. Voluptatem dolores, laudantium qui aspernatur recusandae velit, molestiae facilis harum itaque quisquam! Porro dolorem, pariatur rerum ullam dolores non?</span></p>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tab\" class=\"tab-button\" option=\"f\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 5\">\n                <h3 class=\"tab-head mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">Engagements</h3>\n            </div>\n            <div role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"tab-content\" mbr-if=\"tabsAmount > 5\">\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mbr-white mbr-light\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                    EFFECTIVE ENGAGEMENT\n                </h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-white align-center\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><span>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Dignissimos, pariatur omnis odit, molestias inventore beatae adipisci fugiat fugit itaque minus explicabo iure deserunt corporis minima vitae dicta et libero sit.</span><span>Nihil cumque aspernatur nam fugiat iusto error, distinctio, dolorum explicabo nobis. Voluptatem dolores, laudantium qui aspernatur recusandae velit, molestiae facilis harum itaque quisquam! Porro dolorem, pariatur rerum ullam dolores non?</span></p>\n            </div>\n        </amp-selector>\n    </div>\n\n</section>",
